ACTITECT & RBDISCO LICENSE
==========================

Preamble
--------
This repository contains two kinds of artifacts:

1. Source code (Python modules, scripts, utilities)
2. Pretrained models and weights (in `models/` and related directories)

These are governed by different licenses:

- Code is licensed under the PolyForm Noncommercial License 1.0.0
- Models are licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0 International License (CC BY-NC-SA 4.0)
- Third-party dependencies (installed via PyPI) retain their own original licenses.

Commercial use of either code or models is not permitted without explicit permission from the authors.


